OL,3,CPolice actions under investigation
OL,4,Cfollowing allegations against former
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,8,Finto the way police in Northern
OL,9,FIreland managed allegations of
OL,10,Finappropriate conduct made against a
OL,11,Fformer police officer while he was
OL,12,Fstill in the role.
OL,14,FThe Police Ombudsman said the new
OL,15,Finvestigation is linked to an ongoing
OL,16,Fcase in which the former officer was
OL,17,Farrested in December 2025 on suspicion
OL,18,Fof committing a number of sexual
OL,19,Foffences including rape.
