OL,7,FPolice Ombudsman chief executive Hugh
OL,8,FHume said: "This investigation centres
OL,9,Fon how a number of allegations made
OL,10,Fagainst the police officer were
OL,11,Fhandled at that time.
OL,13,F"These are sensitive issues and those
OL,14,Fwho made allegations did so in
OL,15,Fdifficult circumstances.
OL,17,F"My priority is to ensure that their
OL,18,Fvoices remain at the centre of the
OL,19,Finvestigation as it progresses."
